---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <span class="text-wave-pink font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">My Story</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-wave-blue-dark mt-2">A little bit about me</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Decorative circle background -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-full bg-wave-blue-light opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <!-- Avatar -->
          <img
            src="/chelseapic.jpeg"
            alt="Chelsea Seymour"
            class="relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 rounded-full object-cover shadow-2xl border-4 border-white"
          />
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 bg-wave-pink text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg">
            Redcliffe, BNE
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-wave-gray leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            My name is Chelsea and I am an age-group triathlete who has absolutely fallen in love
            with the sport. I genuinely believe that big goals are possible even when life is busy.
            I work full time, I train around shift work, and I know firsthand what it takes to
            balance it all. With my experience and knowledge I'd love to help more people achieve
            their goals and become more confident in the water.
          </p>
          <p>
            Something I've noticed is that triathletes have the engine, but they lack the 'feel'
            for the water. With a lifelong background in National-level competitive swimming, I see
            the technical gaps that fitness alone can't fix.
          </p>
          <p>
            I provide 1:1 swim analysis, 1:1 swimming lessons and triathlon programming designed to
            turn your 'weakest' leg into your most consistent. Let's bridge the gap between your
            effort and your results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tags -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
          {[
            'National-Level Swimmer',
            '1:1 Swim Analysis',
            'Triathlon Programming',
            'Redcliffe Local',
          ].map(tag => (
            <span class="bg-wave-blue-light text-wave-blue text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
